Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝毫未变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 甲贺人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部半藏大人的府邸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺胧 可以进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是第二代半藏正就之子 响八郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现为第四代半藏正广的养子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你不会记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将你们一族逼入绝地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必 你对我们恨之入骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无奈君命难违
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 可有佩刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽无铭 却是把好刀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺弦之介情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强能维持清醒状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就尽早进行 只要能站着就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是疾风迅雷一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到仅仅十日便迎来如此惨淡结局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严酷的冬季终将结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来一直渴盼这个季节的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 平静祥和的一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们前往伊势的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正碰上见证这场对决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这完全事出偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场决斗我们并未动任何手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望身为双方忍众仲裁的您亲眼证实这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必在家康大人御前为此作证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲…甲贺弦之介被伊贺封闭双目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并身负重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那也算忍术之争的结果范畴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本该如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才您的喋喋不休
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那反而会招致不必要的怀疑 阿福夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然事到如今 也无力为你做很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙您盛意 有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请您代为保管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是与锷隐十人颇有渊源之物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的…祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下定当妥善保管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我败了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕 那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺弦之介 那种状态下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少痛快地一刀送他上路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧 赶快杀了那个甲贺人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜欢您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…来人 来人杀了弦之介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那二人 莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响八郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后写下此文的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃伊贺忍者 胧是也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这最终局面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:18:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟以这种方式决定伊贺和竹千代一方的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是邪运超强的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伊贺赢了 送去骏府城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为清风吹拂之时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同镌梦想于心之时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有偶然想到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人与我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很久以前 也许是同一个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分为二的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许渴望回复原来的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 我才对弦之介大人这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是同一个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定相互吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论经历多少世 无论度过多少夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定
